## Checklists

### Adding a New Config Section

When adding a new configuration section:

- [ ] **Schema**: Add to `templates/config/config.schema.json.template`
- [ ] **Defaults**: Add to `RECOMMENDED_DEFAULTS` in config handler
- [ ] **Type-specific**: Add to `PROJECT_TYPE_DEFAULTS` if only for certain project types
- [ ] **Health-Check**: Add check function if section needs validation
- [ ] **Docs**: Update relevant skill reference docs

### Adding a New Hook

When adding a new hook:

- [ ] **Config**: Add `hooks.<name>` section to schema
- [ ] **Handler**: Create handler in events layer
- [ ] **Prompts**: Add customizable prompts in config
- [ ] **Tests**: Add tests for handler
- [ ] **Docs**: Document in skill reference

### Modifying Managed Files

When changing managed files:

- [ ] **Template**: Update in `templates/` directory
- [ ] **Schema**: Update `managed.*` in schema if new category
- [ ] **Sync**: Verify with `/dk plugin check`

